msgstr "<phrase>Novo projeto do &LabPlot;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1310 index.docbook:1535
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guilabel>Project</guilabel> item on the <guilabel>Project "
"Explorer</guilabel> panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Add "
"new</guimenu><guimenuitem>Worksheet</guimenuitem></menuchoice> or press "
"<keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> on the keyboard."
msgstr ""
"Clique no item <guilabel>Projeto</guilabel> do painel <guilabel>Explorador "
"de Projetos</guilabel> com o &RMB; e escolha <menuchoice><guimenu>Adicionar "
"novo</guimenu><guimenuitem>Folha de Trabalho</guimenuitem></menuchoice> ou "
"pressione <keycombo>&Alt;<keycap>X</keycap></keycombo> no teclado."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1314 index.docbook:1539
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding new &LabPlot; worksheet</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Adicionar uma nova folha de trabalho do &LabPlot;</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1320 index.docbook:1545
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding new &LabPlot; worksheet</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Adicionar uma nova folha de trabalho do &LabPlot;</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1326
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guilabel>Worksheet</guilabel> item on the <guilabel>Project "
"Explorer</guilabel> panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Add "
"new</guimenu><guisubmenu>xy-plot</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>two axes, "
"centered</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Clique no item <guilabel>Folha de Trabalho</guilabel> no painel "
"<guilabel>Explorador de Projetos</guilabel> com o &RMB; e escolha "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Adicionar novo</guimenu><guisubmenu>gráfico-xy</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>dois eixos, centralizado</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1330 index.docbook:1555
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding axes to the plot</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Adicionar eixos ao gráfico</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1336 index.docbook:1561
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding axes to the plot</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Adicionar eixos ao gráfico</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1342
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click on the <guilabel>xy-plot</guilabel> item on the <guilabel>Project "
"Explorer</guilabel> panel with the &RMB; and choose <menuchoice><guimenu>Add "
"new</guimenu><guimenuitem>xy-curve from a mathematical equation</"
"guimenuitem></menuchoice>."
msgstr ""
"Clique no item <guilabel>gráfico-xy</guilabel> no painel "
"<guilabel>Explorador de Projetos</guilabel> com o &RMB; e escolha "
"<menuchoice> <guimenu>Adicionar novo</guimenu><guimenuitem>curva-xy de uma "
"equação matemática</guimenuitem></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:1346 index.docbook:1571
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>Adding new curve</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>Adicionar nova curva</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:1352 index.docbook:1577
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>Adding new curve</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>Adicionar nova curva</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:1358
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <guilabel>xy-equation-curve properties</guilabel> pane on the right "
"to enter <userinput>sin(x)</userinput> into the <guilabel>y=f(x)</guilabel> "
"field (for the list of available functions please see <xref linkend=\"parser"
